Usage policy
============

 uses the , which involve basically:

 1. Free Transit
 2. Open Communication
 3. No Warranty
 4. Terms of Use
 5. Local Amendments

Points 2 and 3 have been strongly supported during our [[first meeting|meetings/2012-02-15-intro/]], while point #1 was not necessarily supported, some having the idea of running VPN-based connectivity services on top of the mesh, like the Opennet initiative does. Terms of use were not discussed explicitly.

Politiques techniques
=====================

On s'attend à ce que les nodes qui joignent le réseau respectent ces conventions d'utilisation générales.

 * [[numbering]] - comment les addresses IPs sont allouées dans le mesh, liste des IPs allouées
 * [[naming]] - comment les réseaux, machines et services sont nommés dans le mesh
 * [[topology]] - l'architecture générale du réseau
